{
  "texts": [
    "Within the category of \"weak AI,\" 2 primary subfields are prominent: expert systems and machine learning (ML) [6].",
    "Expert systems, categorized under \"symbolic AI,\" operate based on predefined rules and instructions set by human experts [7].",
    "In contrast, ML represents the \"statistical AI\" subfield [8].",
    "ML focuses on pattern recognition within large data sets, enabling the system to learn and make predictions or decisions based on the data [9].",
    "A notable example of such advancements in \"statistical AI\" is the development of large language models, such as ChatGPT, which demonstrate the evolving capabilities of AI in understanding and generating humanlike text, offering new possibilities, and raising unique ethical considerations in their application [10].Despite the significant technological advances in the field of AI and, in particular, \"weak AI,\" \"strong AI,\" which would entail cognitive abilities on par with human intelligence across diverse areas, remains largely theoretical with no substantial application in medicine to date [11]."
  ]
}